ng with W\" title=\"Browse Christian personal names beginning with W\" href=\"/names/christian/letter/W/1\">W</a><a class=\"w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg text-sm font-bold transition-all duration-200 bg-white border border-blue-200 text-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-50 hover:shadow-sm hover:scale-110 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-600\" aria-label=\"Christian names starting with X\" title=\"Browse Christian personal names beginning with X\" href=\"/names/christian/letter/X/1\">X</a><a class=\"w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg text-sm font-bold transition-all duration-200 bg-white border border-blue-200 text-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-50 hover:shadow-sm hover:scale-110 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-600\" aria-label=\"Christian names starting with Y\" title=\"Browse Christian personal names beginning with Y\" href=\"/names/christian/letter/Y/1\">Y</a><a class=\"w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg text-sm font-bold transition-all duration-200 bg-white border border-blue-200 text-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-50 hover:shadow-sm hover:scale-110 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-600\" aria-label=\"Christian names starting with Z\" title=\"Browse Christian personal names beginning with Z\" href=\"/names/christian/letter/Z/1\">Z</a></div></div><div class=\"mb-6 last:mb-0 bg-orange-50 dark:bg-gray-700/30 rounded-2xl p-4 md:p-5\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-orange-700 text-white text-sm font-bold shadow-sm\">🕉️</span><h3 class=\"text-base font-bold text-orange-700\">Hindu<!-- --> Names by Letter</h3><a class=\"ml-auto text-xs font-semibold text-orange-700 hover:underline\" href=\"/names/religion/hindu/1\">View All →</a></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-1.5\"><a class=\"w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg text-sm font-bold transition-all duration-200 bg-white border border-orange-200 text-o